workout_items.name: Conditioning
workout_items.info:
4 x 400m Run with 90s rest in between each round

Look to perform this at 80-100% of your current capacity. 

It might take it right out of you but will be key in the long run... no pun intended.

workout_items.name: Middle Splits - Stage 1
workout_items.info:
We're continuing on with the same hip opening sequence. If you were a bit tight last week, note where you managed to get to and match or slightly increase it this week. 

- 10 Side To Sides each leg
- Standing Pancake
- 10 Side To Sides each leg
- Side Lean each leg ( 1 min )
- Pigeon Hold each leg (2 mins)
